completion_data.completion_summary: Implemented Phase 2 saturation infrastructure for FDSM multi-history construction. Added buildWitnessHistory (using Lindenbaum MCS extension), saturation_step (one round of witness addition), and proved key properties including buildWitnessHistory_models_psi and saturation_step_subset. Phases 3-7 remain for fixed-point construction, modal saturation proof, and Completeness.lean integration.
